## 7. Success Metrics (KPIs)

| Metric | Target | How Measured |
|--------|--------|--------------|
| **Time saved per SOW** | 90% reduction in manual data entry | Compare user time before/after |
| **Adoption rate** | 80% of invited users active weekly | Product analytics |
| **Accuracy of extraction** | >95% (validated by users) | User feedback, corrections |
| **Customer satisfaction (CSAT)** | >4.5/5 | In‑app NPS survey |
| **MRR / ARR** | $50k in first 6 months | Stripe/ billing data |

