---

## 9. Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| OpenAI API cost / latency | Use caching, batch processing, fine‑tune smaller model if needed. |
| Data privacy (SOWs contain sensitive info) | Host on AWS with encryption, comply with GDPR/SOC2. |
| Accuracy of extraction | Include human review step; allow users to correct AI output. |
| Adoption barrier | Provide seamless onboarding, import existing SOWs, offer training. |

---

## 10. Conclusion

DeepSOW addresses a critical, validated market need for SOW visibility and management. By combining AI extraction with a powerful dashboard, it empowers teams to move from reactive firefighting to proactive contract governance. The defined features, paired with a robust tech stack (Next.js, shadcn, DynamoDB, FastAPI, OpenAI), ensure a scalable, modern solution ready for market.

